      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that balances refined performance with lasting value. This unit exhibits a clean aesthetic and consistent mechanical integrity, having undergone a thorough professional inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for roadworthiness and comfort. It represents an ideal acquisition for the discerning driver who prioritizes dependable engineering and a well-preserved interior. Detailed service history is available upon request to confirm its history of responsible ownership.",
