      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it! Whether you're heading on a road trip or just commuting, this beauty won't let you down. I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with the basics so it\u2019s ready for its next adventure. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six with its iconic individual throttle bodies. This unit exhibits excellent throttle response and a healthy VANOS system. The chassis integrity is verified, with the essential rear subframe reinforcement already professionally completed. Power is delivered via a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a functional variable M differential lock. The suspension has been optimized with refreshed bushings to maintain factory geometry and sharp turn-in. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals are dialed in for high-RPM performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
