    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered for sale is a 2017 Audi A6 3.0T Quattro Premium Plus in Moonlight Blue Metallic. This vehicle has been well-cared for and remains in solid condition throughout. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals minor road rash on the front valence and a small, professionally touched-up chip on the passenger door. The 19-inch 10-spoke wheels are wrapped in Continental ProContact tires with roughly 6/32\" tread depth remaining. Inside, the Atlas Beige leather interior is clean and free of tears, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All premium features, including the MMI Navigation plus, Bose Surround Sound, and heated steering wheel, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is robust; the 333hp supercharged V6 pulls strongly, and the 8-speed Tiptronic transmission shifts smoothly. A comprehensive service file is included, highlighting a recent 60,000-mile major service which included spark plugs and a brake fluid flush. This is a reliable, high-performance executive sedan that presents beautifully and is ready for the road.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
