      "description": "This vehicle represents a distinguished balance of performance and long-term reliability. Meticulously maintained and presented in commendable condition, it offers a refined driving experience for the discerning owner. Every aspect of its mechanical integrity has been verified to meet our standards, ensuring a seamless transition to its next steward. This is an exceptional opportunity to acquire a premium automobile at a sophisticated valuation.",
      "price": 34900.0,
